  "title": "Combat Evolution: More Execution Animations",
  "description": "Add Execution Animation from EpicFight: Resurrection into Combat Evolution & Fix EpicFight: Resurrection Yamato crash",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@pla_is_me\" title=\"YouTube\">\n    <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/dxehc2hn3/image/upload/v1761811663/youtube_icon_bcbanf.png\" alt=\"YouTube\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\">\n  </a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/EsvPsnqJpz\" title=\"Discord\">\n    <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/dxehc2hn3/image/upload/v1761811736/discord_icon_bg_rp4omx.png\" alt=\"Discord\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\">\n  </a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/pla_is_me\" title=\"Ko‑fi\">\n    <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/dxehc2hn3/image/upload/v1761815764/kofi_icon_bg_sy3foi.png\" alt=\"Ko‑fi\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\">\n  </a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/PlaIsMe\" title=\"github\">\n    <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/dxehc2hn3/image/upload/v1761811682/github_icon_bg_wmtjei.png\" alt=\"Github\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\">\n</a>\n</p>\n\n**Combat Evolution x EpicFight : Resurrection** is an add-on that adds compatibility between **Combat Evolution** and **EpicFight : Resurrection**.\n\nThis mod disables EpicFight: Resurrection's built-in execution system and integrates it with Combat Evolution's execution mechanism, with this mod you can perform execution animation from EpicFight : Resurrection in Combat Evolution Execution mechanism, moreover, the mod fix EpicFight Resurrection Yamato Crash\n\n<p style=\"color:#fc0;font-size:22px;font-weight:bold;text-align:center\">⚠️  This mod is splitted from Annoying Villagers x EpicFight: Resurrection.</p>\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/ito-fUdAimY\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>",
